<br>
Edit: Since there seems to be some confusion on this issue...  The only way to arrange things was to go with another cottage.  There were no other officers around at the time I came up with the arrangement so there was no one to run it by but it seemed logical enough to do.<br>
<br>
So I checked lot prices, did the count-down math, packed up the 'office' stuff I'd purchased with my <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>own</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> funds, logged out near a post in Kingsdale.  Logged in, waited for the prices to drop another notch (and was fairly late for work b/c of it) and purchased a lot and put up a cottage.<br>
<br>
Now I was tooling around with the idea of getting a house anyway once they dropped to 1plat but there was no way to guarentee where it'd be -- not a serious issue for me to be honest -- but as I wasn't going to use the merchant points anyway (well, alb vault but not like I'd need him out all the time) and the guild could use 3 more, it seemed prudent to get one close to the guild houses so that we could have crafting fair w/o going to Diogel to get parts made.  So with that in mind, I purchased early so I could get the spot I chose (listed above) to make things simple.<br>
<br>
To reiterate:  I purchaed <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>my own</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> cottage with <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>my own money</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> and offered the option to open it for guild use. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.silverdaggers.net"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.silverdaggers.net/sigs/vincent1a.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub15.ezboard.com/bdaggersincamelot.showUserPublicProfile?gid=brothervincent>Brother Vincent</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.silverdaggers.net/img/ge.jpg" BORDER=0> at: 7/2/03 10:08 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#871f78><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub15.ezboard.com/bdaggersincamelot.showUserPublicProfile?gid=rhianidd>Rhianidd</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://werzat.freeservers.com/ge.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Human Blade Turn</span><br>  Posts: 1276<br> <font color=#E6E8fA>(7/2/03 5:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub15.ezboard.com/fdaggersincamelotfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1741.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Pricing &amp; Guild Fund: Your Comments Required</span><hr size=1> Looks good to me, Vince.<br>
